      "writtenOn": "2016-09-16T19:12:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "My preference would be to remove the internal locking and instead require the client to synchronize access. Similar to maps and most other Go data structures.",
      "revId": "c3af601e376c250db0d19a7b86a877ef111689e5",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "10261bad_0a414b3c",
        "filename": "task_scheduler/go/scheduling/specs.go",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 253,
      "author": {
        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-09-19T12:25:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I really prefer to have the struct be thread-safe, given that it\u0027s used in several places throughout the flow. I realize that this pattern is awkward; I guess I could change the call site from this:\n\ntcc.Lock()\ndefer tcc.Unlock()\n\nrv :\u003d []\nfor rs, name :\u003d complicated_recursive_thing {\n  rv \u003d append(rv, tcc.GetTaskSpec_Locked(rs, name)\n}\n\nTo this:\n\nts :\u003d []\nfor rs, name :\u003d complicated_recursive_thing {\n  ts \u003d append(ts, (rs, name))\n}\nrv :\u003d tcc.GetTaskSpecs(ts)\n\n?",
      "parentUuid": "10261bad_3f6c4b31",
      "revId": "c3af601e376c250db0d19a7b86a877ef111689e5",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "10261bad_ca535308",
        "filename": "task_scheduler/go/scheduling/specs.go",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 253,
      "author": {
        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-09-19T12:56:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Seems like a good solution. I don\u0027t see a downside, and the upside is that the lock is taken for a shorter duration.",
      "parentUuid": "10261bad_0a414b3c",
      "revId": "c3af601e376c250db0d19a7b86a877ef111689e5",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "10261bad_6ae0bf1f",
        "filename": "task_scheduler/go/scheduling/specs.go",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 253,
